This is a simple implementation for HMM using boost ulas libary.
Please refer to the paperi:A Revealing Introduction to Hidden Markov Models
for more details.

INSTALL:
first, please make sure get boost installed.
and run the following commad lines:
cd you_path_to_HMM/
make
and then run:
./hmm 2 3

The first parameter dentoes the number of state and
the second denotes the number of the Observation symbols.

If you encount any problems, please contact me:

time.clifford@gmail.com



